text: Yang mi pen thi pracaksʹ chad kæ phwk khea dxk hrux wa kimaknxy læw rea di thalay prachachati kxn hna phwk khea hlay chaw stwrrsʹ doythi phwk khea (ku fa rmak kah) di pi phbhen ma nı thi phanak xasay khxng phwk khea thæcring nı kar lngthosʹ chen nan hæla pen nithasn xu tha ha rn sahrab brrda phu mi stipayya
